languages.text: "Агентура докладывает, что недовольные активно ведут общение с обитателями пустошей, остатками так называемого клана бригадиров. И те даже готовы оказать им поддержку".
"Agents report that the disgruntled are actively negotiating with the wasteland dwellers — the remains of the so-called foreman clan. And it seems they are willing to offer their support."

languages.text: “您的特工报告说，一部分心怀不满的人正在积极与废土居民谈判。那些居民正是警督氏族的残党，而且他们似乎愿意提供支持。”
languages.original_text: "Agents report that the disgruntled are actively negotiating with the wasteland dwellers — the remains of the so-called brigadier clan. And it seems they are willing to offer their support."

languages.text: «Los agentes informan de que los inconformistas están negociando activamente con los habitantes del páramo, los restos del llamado clan de los brigadistas. Y parece que están dispuestos a ofrecer su apoyo».
languages.original_text: "Agents report that the disgruntled are actively negotiating with the wasteland dwellers — the remains of the so-called brigadier clan. And it seems they are willing to offer their support."

languages.text: 「諜報員の報告によると、不満を抱いた者達は、ウエストランドの住人...いわゆる准将一族の残党とは積極的に交渉しているようだ。しかも、力を惜しまず支援しようとしている」
languages.original_text: "Agents report that the disgruntled are actively negotiating with the wasteland dwellers — the remains of the so-called brigadier clan. And it seems they are willing to offer their support."

languages.text: « Des agents signalent que les mécontents négocient activement avec les habitants des terres désolées... enfin, avec ce qui reste du clan des Brigadiers. Il semble qu'ils soient prêts à leur prêter main-forte. »
languages.original_text: "Agents report that the disgruntled are actively negotiating with the wasteland dwellers — the remains of the so-called brigadier clan. And it seems they are willing to offer their support."

languages.text: "Agenten berichten, dass die unzufriedenen Bürger aktiv mit den Bewohnern des Ödlands verhandeln, den Überresten des so genannten Brigadierclans. Und offenbar sind sie bereit, ihre Unterstützung anzubieten."
